Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌的梦…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTA------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.99,0:01:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.35,0:01:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安 西蒙妮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.54,0:02:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这女人无论如何熬夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.26,0:02:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是比我先起床 开始工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.07,0:02:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝说去剑道部晨练了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.45,0:02:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.70,0:02:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1 2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.43,0:02:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,600)}1 2 1 2…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.79,0:02:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙妮 看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.12,0:02:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.63,0:03:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期中考试都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们却一点都没迸发呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迸…迸发？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.75,0:03:15.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迸发什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚 难得跟老公通电话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.02,0:03:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现他旁边有个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.91,0:03:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我也有不是 长期不在他身边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.38,0:03:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渡边加奈子夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我服侍的太太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年纪轻轻就已挑起世界经济的大梁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力着实厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝非等闲之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.22,0:03:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.18,0:03:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说红杏出墙的原因排行榜上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「报复外遇的丈夫」总是名列前茅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.13,0:03:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在深有同感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深有同感的我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.49,0:03:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非也是同类？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:04:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 拓人君 你有何想法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我讨厌这个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 期中考试也结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天放学后在我家游船泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,举行1班亲睦派对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.23,0:04:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都来迸发下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没鳄鱼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:39.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扬卷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.87,0:04:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:05:03.39,INCN4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,300)\blur4}柔和阳光下 绽开的蓓蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.56,0:05:11.62,INCN4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,500)\blur4}小睡之中 感受着喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:19.72,INCN4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,300)\blur4}触到了觉醒的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:26.48,INCN4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(100,300)\blur4}好似初始的清晨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:32.14,INCN4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,300)\blur4}遍地的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:36.26,INCN4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,300)\blur4}是升空的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:40.04,INCN4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(100,200)\blur4}数亿的生息
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:48.36,INCN4,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,300)\blur4}此刻 世界转世重生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.07,0:05:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 好岛啊 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和子的歌很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又迷上她了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉璃 你这泳装好大胆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比不上石野老师呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 这是家庭访问
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白吗 家庭访问 家庭访问
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.74,0:06:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.85,0:06:30.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩史君好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.84,0:06:35.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次的事 记忆犹新呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你擅长二刀流？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要再比一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 比起拿竹刀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.77,0:06:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你更适合弹钢琴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.02,0:06:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 须方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这公园里遇见人还是头一遭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们学园的学生？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.56,0:07:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没怎么见过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里能把岛上最美丽的夕阳尽收眼底
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是画家？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没了想画的题材
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以暂时搁置了画笔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.42,0:07:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很烦人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑子里想着不要再画了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.75,0:07:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是还没问世的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后即将诞生的画
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.21,0:07:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直嚷嚷着要我快点让它出世呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.93,0:07:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想出来的话 就放它出来好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.32,0:07:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神赐予人的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有他的意义吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用它或许是罪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.50,0:08:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你住附近？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.02,0:08:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再在附近遇见我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得打声招呼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.53,0:08:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个俊美的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是个美少年 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.41,0:08:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主张所有素体所有权的成人银行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是在扩大解释规则吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.01,0:08:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理素体
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等于要对全人类负上沉重的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须是正确理解这点的人才能胜任
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.86,0:08:39.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以认为这女人非等闲之辈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因为这种场合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来她似乎是真的在考虑世界和平
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好听
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 听说成人银行的行长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很早就曾把素体挪作私用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把素体挪作私用？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.37,0:09:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我还是头一次听说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果这是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.34,0:09:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我或许就太抬举她了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.04,0:09:18.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人 老爷打来了电话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是庆祝结婚纪念日
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他竟还记得结婚纪念日 真不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.35,0:09:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 告诉他我待会儿再打过去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)\fad(0,400)}（你好 我是西蒙妮…）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.53,0:09:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}与我通话的这个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是格兰·托奈尔财团的现党首
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.50,0:09:42.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷昂·渡边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.17,0:09:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈子的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是我的亲生父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个事实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈子 孝以及雷昂·渡边都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是直到去年才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:10:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 那刚好是一年前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遇到交通事故的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好没有大伤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.49,0:10:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保险起见还是住院检查了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时病房的电视里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在播雷昂·渡边的新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年过60的财阀党首
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与和我年龄相仿 名叫加奈子的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚的新闻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而来探望我的姐姐米蕾娜看了以后说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在电视上那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.57,0:10:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我们的亲生父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.50,0:10:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一无所知 在母子单亲家庭长大的我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那时第一次知道了自己出生的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的母亲梅利珊德曾经是雷昂·渡边的秘书
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许很老套吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.14,0:10:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲不知不觉成了他的情妇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.54,0:11:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生了两个女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是姐姐米蕾娜和我 帕梅拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐米蕾娜要我去当这个加奈子的秘书
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.19,0:11:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是我隐藏身份
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化名西蒙妮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,0:11:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去接近抛弃母亲的男人的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去战斗一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.42,0:11:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素体可以复原了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孝的Tzadikt也可以再战了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要赢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.96,0:11:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爬到那女人的头上去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 就算Tzadikt修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我已经被剥夺了徽章（Emblem）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 我有个提议
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.92,0:11:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能出动西蒙妮的Dalethos（扉）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:55.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有孝这样的战斗能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 驾驶交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.75,0:12:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西蒙妮驯化后的Dalethos
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以交给我自由驾驭吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要做那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.36,0:12:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你在这里不是为了战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 今晚还有特别的朋友要来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女人表现出动摇 真是稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.71,0:12:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.47,0:12:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生怕我成为首领 慌了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.34,0:12:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有资格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.42,0:13:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细想来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.08,0:13:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一年间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起看镜中的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.94,0:13:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注视着那个女人的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多出许多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人 真的慌了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.02,0:13:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.64,0:13:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社团开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.80,0:13:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可有意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.74,0:13:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要一炮走红了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天看了你们戏剧部的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.01,0:13:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 好像偷窥似的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.00,0:13:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢所以才一直看 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.19,0:14:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为喜欢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 有那么点意外
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.23,0:14:23.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方演戏的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.87,0:14:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中学的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还演过独角戏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.24,0:14:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没多久还有了粉丝团
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.71,0:14:36.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.92,0:14:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很擅长扮演分配来的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.35,0:14:47.79,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}喜欢这翠色的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.40,0:14:54.74,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}风又带来夏天的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.15,0:14:57.95,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}千回辗转
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:15:00.99,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(100,200)\blur4}万回闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.14,0:15:05.65,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}光就这样诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:24.02,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}阳光融化在天空的另一侧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.24,0:15:29.67,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(130,300)\blur4}哪里都是透明的蓝色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.23,0:15:36.21,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}加速的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.22,0:15:42.61,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}现在以自己的意志飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:49.09,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}流出去的水的行踪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:52.74,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,300)\blur4}放飞自己的心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:58.23,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}喜欢这翠色的季节
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.91,0:16:04.50,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}风又带来夏天的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.93,0:16:10.19,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}伤痕等会就会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:17.15,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,400)\blur4}开始溢出的热情的交响乐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:20.47,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}千回辗转
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.67,0:16:23.38,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(100,200)\blur4}万回闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:28.03,INCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fad(200,200)\blur4}光就这样诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.22,0:15:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开启 电气柩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.16,0:15:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打算干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.95,0:16:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘书（Secretary）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我进入你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.91,0:16:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.18,0:16:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把素体中驭星者的能力作为武器使用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是猩红之吻以失败告终的战术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次进入驾驶舱的银行家（Banker）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与电气柩中的秘书是协同作战
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与猩红之吻当时性质完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.39,0:16:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驯化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.94,0:17:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飒爽登场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.02,0:17:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tauburn
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星剑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紫水晶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到 能兼用银行家的星剑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.59,0:17:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操纵的也是银行家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.87,0:17:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她参战合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星剑 翡翠
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星剑 蓝宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.45,0:17:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 秘书
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只须把能量全部集中在这把剑上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:18:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而操作全部交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.10,0:18:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 二刀流
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事 那把剑的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘剑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.23,0:18:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纸吹雪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样 秘书
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能赢 能赢 银行家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.66,0:18:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这对组合的平衡性可能不错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能赢吗 面对银河美少年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.87,0:18:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 一决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自以为能赢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.35,0:19:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二对一有失公允
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.69,0:19:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 须方君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.52,0:19:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话有搞头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.04,0:19:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:06.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多此一举吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.16,0:20:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.23,0:20:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 万一又陷入永眠的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.84,0:20:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能是神的馈赠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,须方君…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.02,0:20:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心孝的安全 放弃了战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.81,0:20:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样便好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腥风血雨不适合你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.82,0:20:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.51,0:20:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜是我的挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.44,0:20:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好屋子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.72,0:20:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看下身体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:20:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.52,0:21:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几乎没留下痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.60,0:21:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我送来这里 不是为了复仇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年前 你遇到交通事故昏迷的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见悲痛欲绝的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.63,0:21:16.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加奈子为救你 驯化了素体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.04,0:21:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说成人银行的行长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很早就曾把素体挪作私用
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈和加奈子认识？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把加奈子介绍给雷昂·渡边作为合伙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.96,0:21:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许比起自己的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.01,0:21:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时更需要加奈子的才能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.61,0:21:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.19,0:21:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.08,0:21:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就知道西蒙妮是我的假名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.28,0:21:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么装作不知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.01,0:22:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是蛮喜欢这种情形的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.92,0:22:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.31,0:22:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈夫情妇的女儿改名换姓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.12,0:22:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潜伏在自己身边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.36,0:22:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗地里对我咬牙切齿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.52,0:22:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相当浪漫有情调啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.90,0:22:24.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最讨厌这女人
Comment: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.90,0:24:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人妻女高生终于发来了约会邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.20,0:24:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去吗 还是去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.36,0:24:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要自重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.66,0:24:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 驭星者
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.10,0:24:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔着玻璃的吻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.46,0:24:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.53,0:24:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐喊吧 驯化…
